<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-block_role">Role: UX, UI Design, HTML/CSS</p>
    <p class="text-block_copy">With all of the statistics, devices, and apps available today, it's becoming harder to be noticed in the inbox. While working as a Lead UI Designer at AWeber, we realized our customers needed a way to make automated email campaigns that could be triggered based on subscribers engagement with their messages. Time is a precious thing and our customers want to be spending it developing business, not micromanaging email.</p>
</section>

