<section class="text-block">
    <h3 class="text-block_title">Challenge</h3>
    <p class="text-block_copy">While designing for this new feature in our application, it was important to work with our developers to understand technical capabilities. Our application was 16 years old and carried a lot of technical baggage. We had to redesign not only the UI but a majority of the backend functionality as well.</p>
     
    <p class="text-block_copy">From a UX standpoint, we also needed to consider how this would affect our users' workflow. We were introducing an entirely new user flow so one of our main focus while creating this new feature is how to education and re-teach our users.</p> 
</section>

